    <title>清华托福慕课</title>
    <link href="/2021/08/12/%E6%89%98%E7%A6%8F%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87-b%E7%AB%99/"/>
    <url>/2021/08/12/%E6%89%98%E7%A6%8F%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87-b%E7%AB%99/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- toc --><ul><li><a href="#%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB">阅读</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B">听力</a><ul><li><a href="#%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B51-10%E5%A4%A9-top1-5">阶段1 10天 TOP1-5</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B52-5%E5%A4%A9-top6-10">阶段2 5天 TOP6-10</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B53-5%E5%A4%A9-sss-%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BAhttpswwwscientificamericancompodcasts">阶段3 5天 SSS <a href="https://www.scientificamerican.com/podcasts/">科学美国人</a></a></li><li><a href="#%E8%AF%8D%E6%80%A7-%E5%8F%91%E9%9F%B3%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82">词性-&gt;发音差异</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%91%E9%9F%B3">常用简化发音</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E6%80%A7%E7%9F%AD%E8%AF%AD">习惯性短语</a></li><li><a href="#conversation">Conversation</a><ul><li><a href="#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF">常见场景</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB">层次关系</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%80%83%E7%82%B9">常见考点</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#lecture">Lecture</a><ul><li><a href="#lecture%E4%B8%8E%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB">Lecture与阅读的关系</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84">常见结构</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%80%83%E7%82%B9-1">常见考点</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#%E8%AE%B0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95">记笔记方法</a></li><li><a href="#%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%AD%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%88%B0%E8%B4%A8%E5%8F%98">结语：量变到质变</a></li></ul></li></ul><!-- tocstop --><h1><span id="阅读">阅读</span></h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2021-08-08%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%887.41.41.png"></p><h1><span id="听力">听力</span></h1><p>每天3小时，一个月</p><h2><span id="阶段1-10天-top1-5">阶段1       10天 TOP1-5</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.01.54%20AM.png"></p><ol><li>盲听一遍</li><li>按句听，完全还原每一句话所有单词（非常严格，吞音也要还原）（如果听不出来看原文）</li><li>把生词加入生词本</li><li>逐句听，模仿发音，包括所有发音特征 （5-10遍）</li><li>整体再听一遍，达标</li></ol><h2><span id="阶段2-5天-top6-10">阶段2        5天 TOP6-10</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.10.44%20AM.png"></p><ol><li>盲听两遍</li><li>拿着脚本听，对</li><li>生词</li><li>影子跟读（3-5遍）</li><li>整体再听一遍，达标</li></ol><h2><span id="阶段3-5天-sss-科学美国人">阶段3        5天 SSS </span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.14.59%20AM.png"></p><p>SSS：帮你带入真正美国课堂的语速</p><ol><li>盲听2-3遍</li><li>对应脚本每个词</li><li>影子跟读</li><li>听一遍</li></ol><p><a href="open.163.com/ocw">泛听</a></p><h2><span id="词性-gt发音差异">词性-&gt;发音差异</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.23.07%20AM.png"></p><p>动词会把音放在中间</p><h2><span id="常用简化发音">常用简化发音</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.24.52%20AM.png"></p><h2><span id="习惯性短语">习惯性短语</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.26.50%20AM.png"></p><h2><span id="conversation">Conversation</span></h2><h3><span id="常见场景">常见场景</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.28.59%20AM.png"></p><p>教授、员工特别负责，并且严格</p><p>女同学什么都做得好，</p><p>男同学一直听不懂，论文一直都写不好</p><p>实验永远都是操作有问题</p><p>加分、选课、毕业修分</p><h3><span id="层次关系">层次关系</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.33.45%20AM.png"></p><ul><li>Conversation</li><li>一般4-6个 layer </li><li>往往有一个主题</li><li>听清楚 case A， 是✅还是❌， 如何导出的case b</li></ul><h3><span id="常见考点">常见考点</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/Screen%20Shot%202021-08-04%20at%209.36.13%20AM.png"></p><h2><span id="lecture">Lecture</span></h2><h3><span id="lecture与阅读的关系">Lecture与阅读的关系</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357015.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.43.31 AM"></p><h3><span id="常见结构">常见结构</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357587.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.45.59 AM"></p><h3><span id="常见考点">常见考点</span></h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357380.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.47.38 AM"></p><h2><span id="记笔记方法">记笔记方法</span></h2><p>先左右分开，或者分三列</p><p>根据层次递进地听、记，最重要的是把层次听出来</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357766.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.49.06 AM"></p><p>并不是所有人都适合一开始就记笔记，如果一开始连一半都听不懂记笔记反而成为负担</p><p>大多数人是需要记笔记的</p><p>辅助记录，分析层次，答题时不需要回看笔记的</p><p>如果有人不加试，旁边的人会已经开始口语，影响自己注意力</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357519.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.52.43 AM"></p><h2><span id="结语量变到质变">结语：量变到质变</span></h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/geminigby/drawing-bed-1/raw/master/202108112357709.png" alt="Screen Shot 2021-08-04 at 9.55.35 AM"></p><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>原视频地址：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LW411v7Z6">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LW411v7Z6</a><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
